==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Doubtfulness
<hw>Doubt"ful*ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <sn>1.</sn> <def>State of being
doubtful.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>2.</sn> <def>Uncertainty of meaning; ambiguity;
indefiniteness.</def> ⟦ldquo⟧ The <xex>doubtfulness</xex> of his
expressions.⟦rdquo⟧ <rj><au>Locke.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><sn>3.</sn> <def>Uncertainty of event or issue.</def>
<rj><au>Bacon.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Doubting</ent>⟦br⟧
